+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                              |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: l DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=25                                                                                                                |
